as large as NASA=E2=80=99s. And like NASA did with its COTS program a decad=
e ago, NNSA is now turning to public-private partnerships to modernize its =
nuclear testing capabilities.=C2=A0
As SpaceX is to NASA, Fuse wants to be to the NNSA.=C2=A0
Most fusion startups are trying to fly straight to Mars, so to speak, witho=
