Eventually, Fuse believes that cheaper and more performant capacitors will =
lead to cheaper and more performant pulsed-power generators which will lead=
 to MagLIF generators that produce more energy from fusion reactions than i=
s put into those reactions, profitably. Fusion power baby!=C2=A0
Now, with a little physics under our belt, we can turn to what Fuse is buil=
