-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Use that supply chai=
n to solve the bottlenecks to profitable fusion, like capacitor life.</p></=
li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=
=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-h=
eight: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Begin selling=
 power with a fusion-fission generator that uses nuclear waste as fuel and =
has less extreme requirements than pure fusion.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"=
margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: =
border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; mar=
gin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Build profitable fusion gener=
ators and put them in every city on earth.&#160;</p></li><li style=3D"margi=
n: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: borde=
r-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: =
0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">Maybe, one day, power interstellar=
 travel with fusion engines.&#160;</p></li></ul><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, =
55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The busin=
ess machine fits together so perfectly it almost feels as if it were pre-or=
dained, a gift from a cosmic entity who wants us to pass through the Great =
Filter.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-=
height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">To understand how it all fits together a=
nd why Fuse may be able to pull off a goal that&#8217;s eluded so many bril=
liant people, we&#8217;re going to need to go deep. My hope is that by divi=
ng into the details, you&#8217;ll emerge with an appreciation for how beaut=
ifully the whole machine works. I&#8217;ve known JC for over a year and did=
 a whole podcast season on nuclear fission and fusion, and I still had a fe=
w, &#8220;holy shit no way&#8221; moments writing this piece.&#160;&#160;</=
p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;">We&#8217;ll cover a wide range of topics from fusion ba=
sics to nuclear weapons testing to the many uses of radiation. We&#8217;ll =
navigate government budgets and national labs. We&#8217;ll even do a little=
 SpaceX comparison, which, by the end, might not seem as absurd as it sound=
s.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">What makes Fuse unique is that it&#8217;s try=
ing to optimize for an entire system that predictably and profitably moves =
towards fusion power instead of optimizing for the platonic ideal of a fusi=
on generator. </p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line=
-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Fuse&#8217;s generator design, customer=
 needs, and business model are intricately linked; one stage flows into and=
 funds the next. If it works, Fuse will be the rare capital efficient fusio=
n company.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; li=
ne-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">But a plan is just a plan. While Fuse=
 has made impressive progress, building three generators on time and on bud=
get and signing government contracts in just five years on $20 million, it =
will have to build bigger and more powerful machines, run multiple interlin=
ked businesses, and sell to a variety of customers, including various US Go=
vernment agencies, to earn the right to sell fusion power.</p><p style=3D"c=
olor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px=
 0;">Like any great company, then, Fuse is a bet on the team. And that star=
ts with JC.&#160;</p><h3 class=3D"header-with-anchor-widget" style=3D"-moz-=
appearance: optimizelegibility; -moz-osx-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webk=
it-appearance: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; app=
