'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 1.375em; font-weight: bold;=
 line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong=
>JC&#8217;s Dream</strong><span>&#160;</span></h3><p style=3D"color: rgb(54=
, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There&#=
8217;s this stereotype of a Great Founder.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(=
54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">A gen=
ius, exposed to big ideas and adult conversations early in life, who shows =
early entrepreneurial signs by building a small business at a young age. A =
precocious outsider who faces some sort of adversity that builds resilience=
 and some critical skill, driven by a burning mission.&#160;</p><p style=3D=
"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0;"><em>Most </em><span>founders don&#8217;t actually fit the stereotype=
 perfectly. JC Btaiche kinda does.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In som=
e ways, JC was like a lot of kids. He dreamed of being an astronaut.</p><p =
style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;">In practically every other way, he wasn&#8217;t.&#160;</p><p=
 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">Born in Saudi Arabia, JC moved to Lebanon when he was littl=
e, where his nuclear physics-trained father pursued his career as a plant m=
anager building manufacturing facilities.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">When h=
e was just seven years old, his eighteen-year-old brother set up a gaming l=
ounge with four computers on the floor of a building in their village, and =
JC helped out. When his brother left for Canada the next year, eight-year-o=
ld JC took over the business. He hosted Counter-Strike and Dota tournaments=
, sold crepes and hot dogs, and attracted paying customers from as far as a=
n hour away. When money came in, he used it to buy new computers, scaling f=
rom 4 to 32 during his time at the helm.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54=
, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>&=
#8220;It was a full business,&#8221; he </span><a href=3D"https://substack.=
com/redirect/d5ab27c2-8fd5-4490-b8ab-b94bceea08e1?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb=
8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, =
55); text-decoration: underline;">said</a><span>, &#8220;It was a large par=
t of the family&#8217;s income.&#8221;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: r=
gb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">At=
 night, dinner conversations with his nuclear physicist father sparked JC&#=
8217;s interest in understanding how the universe worked. Not in a superfic=
ial or theoretical way. He wanted to be an astronaut because he wanted to g=
o see the universe for himself, to prove that what people said about it was=
 actually true.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Imagine little JC&#8217;s disapp=
ointment, then, when his father told him that no human has actually ever tr=
aveled further than the moon, and that it wasn&#8217;t quite possible to do=
 so.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So he started Googling.&#160;</p><div class=
