olor: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px=
 0;">Humans hadn&#8217;t even figured out how to use fusion to generate pow=
er on earth yet, he learned, let alone to power interstellar travel. So des=
pite the fact that JC didn&#8217;t like school, fusion motivated him to sit=
 in a classroom and pay attention in order to nail the basics. Outside of t=
he classroom, he kept researching fusion.&#160;&#160;</p><p style=3D"color:=
 rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">=
<span>At just 16-years-old, JC got a research internship at the American Un=
iversity of Beirut, where he &#8220;researched the mysterious hexagon on th=
e pole of Saturn in the fluid dynamics and plasma laboratory under the supe=
