aMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-dec=
oration: underline;">podcast</a><span>, he started Hestia because he was de=
eply disappointed by the startups he met at a university accelerator in Mon=
