ne;">Fuse Energy</a><span>.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, =
55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It&#8217;s te=
mpting, and usually too simplistic, to draw straight lines from adolescent =
experiences to something that someone did later in life. But given that JC =
started Fuse at 19-years-old, you don&#8217;t need to draw a very long line=
 to connect his childhood to the company.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(5=
4, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There =
are the obvious ones:&#160;</p><ul style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li=
 style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"bo=
x-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">He&#8217;s starting=
 a fusion company because of a lifelong dream to see the universe.&#160;</p=
></li><li style=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p st=
yle=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; lin=
e-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;">That a 19-=
