iddle; width: 100%;"></a><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16p=
x; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">TITAN I is a vast improvement ov=
er the state of the art pulsed power generators. According to Fuse, it&#821=
7;s 3x more compact, has a 1,000x higher lifetime, is 2x more energy effici=
ent, and at least 5x cheaper than current pulsed energy drivers.&#160;</p><=
p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; marg=
in: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The company showed the world&#8217;s first experimen=
tal results for over 100 consecutive shots of an IMG, and submitted the res=
ults to </span><em>Nature Scientific Reports</em><span> for peer-review. On=
e of the co-authors on the paper is </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/=
