(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><spa=
n>The rabbit holes led the team into &#8220;this really niche, obscure worl=
d where you can&#8217;t find the buyers on LinkedIn or at conferences&#8221=
;: </span><strong>nuclear effects testing</strong><span>.&#160;&#160;</span=
></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The nuclear effects testing market is really three s=
eparate markets:</p><ul style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li style=3D"m=
argin: 8px 0 0 32px; mso-special-format: bullet;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: b=
