 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>During the Cold War, President Raegan advocated for &=
#8220;</span><strong>peace through strength</strong><span>,&#8221; a modern=
 expression of an old military principle advocated by Thucydides, Machiavel=
li, and Teddy Roosevelt, among others. Simply put, the best way to prevent =
another country from attacking America with nuclear weapons is to make it c=
lear that doing so would mean even more catastrophic consequences for their=
 country.&#160;&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-si=
ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">America boasts the world&=
#8217;s largest nuclear arsenal, but most of our nuclear weapons were built=
 between the 1940s and the 1980s. The youngest are forty years old.&#160;</=
p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Given the rising threat, the DoD is undergoing th=
e largest </span><strong>modernization</strong><span> effort in the country=
&#8217;s history. As the Air Force&#8217;s Nuclear Weapons Center wrote in =
a DoD proposal:</span></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px solid #51b4=
e9; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-s=
ize: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em><=
span>The Department of Defense and the Air Force are in the middle of an un=
precedented recapitalization of the ENTIRE nuclear triad to include the wea=
pons themselves. Since the triad was created, this has never occurred in ou=
r history. This investment of </span><strong>over $1 trillion is budgeted, =
funded, and in build, above all other competing requirements and Defense ne=
eds</strong><span>, because it is necessary as the most important global de=
terrent in our arsenal to counter those who wish to dominate the United Sta=
tes and undo our freedoms.</span></em></p></blockquote><p style=3D"color: r=
