ested $2.5 billion for the two projects, $1.8 billion for SCORPIUS and $700=
 million for ZEUS.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font=
-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Unfortunately, accordi=
ng to the Government Accountability Office (GAO), &#8220;Zeus will now be d=
