e team. It&#8217;s also a testament to JC&#8217;s fresh sheet approach to b=
uilding a defense and fusion company.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 5=
5, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>In a=
n internal hiring doc, </span><em>Only In America Could This Be Possible, <=
